SUMMARY:Mulch & Mingle with Partner in Employment (PIE)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Kubota Gardens Natural Area. \nJoin Partner in Employment for a fun-filled community event! \nThis event will be centered on caring for the native plants our fall restoration crews have installed in previous years by laying down mulch around them. We’ll also learn about the amazing benefits and importance of mulch! \nWe would love to see you there 😀 \nRegister
